1.00	St._John's_Convention_Centre	St. John's Convention Centre	The St. John's Convention Centre, located in Downtown St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador at 50 New Gower Street is the province's largest convention centre with 18,200 square feet (1,900 m2) of space. The convention centre was completed in May 2001 along with Mile One Centre, which is located across the road and linked by a pedway system. The centre is also linked with the Delta Hotel, which supplies catering for events.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/47/St._John%27s_Convention_Centre.jpg/250px-St._John%27s_Convention_Centre.jpg
